<dashboard script="example_all.js">
  <label>02. Collection of Views</label>
  <description>한 페이지에 가장 일반적인보기를 표시합니다. 검색 컨트롤을 검색 관리자와 동기화하는 방법과 정적 옵션 및 검색 기반 선택 항목으로 양식 컨트롤을 채우는 방법을 보여줍니다.</description>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
                <p>This example shows how to set up the most common views using JavaScript. Tokens are used to keep the search controls in sync with the search manager.</p>
                <table>
                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 80%;">
                            <h3>SearchBar</h3>
                            <div id="mysearchbar"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 20%;">
                            <h3>TimeRange<br/>(also included with SearchBar)</h3>
                            <div id="mytimerange"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 100%;">
                            <h3>SearchControls</h3>
                            <div id="mysearchcontrols"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>


                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 100%;">
                            <h3>Timeline</h3>
                            <div id="mytimeline"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 100%;">
                            <h3>EventsViewer</h3>
                            <div id="myeventsviewer"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 100%;">
                            <h3>Table</h3>
                            <div id="mytable"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 100%;">
                            <h3>Chart</h3>
                            <div id="mychart"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 33%;">
                            <h3>Single</h3>
                            <div id="mysingle"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 34%;">
                            <h3>TextInput</h3>
                            <div id="mytextinput"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 33%;">
                            <h3>Checkbox</h3>
                            <p>Check me:</p>
                            <div id="mycheckbox"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>CheckboxGroup (static choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mycheckboxgroup1"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>CheckboxGroup (search-based choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mycheckboxgroup2"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>RadioGroup (static choices)</h3>
                            <div id="myradiogroup1"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>RadioGroup (search-based choices)</h3>
                            <div id="myradiogroup2"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>Dropdown (static choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mydropdown1"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>Dropdown (search-based choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mydropdown2"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>


                    <!-- Row -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>MultiDropdown (static choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mymultidropdown1"/>
                        </td>
                        <td style="width: 50%;">
                            <h3>MultiDropdown (search-based choices)</h3>
                            <div id="mymultidropdown2"/>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>